==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Soldiering
<hw>Sol"dier*ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of serving
as a soldier; the state of being a soldier; the occupation of a
soldier.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The act of feigning to work. See the Note under
<er>Soldier</er>, <pos>v. i.</pos>, 2.</def> <mark>[Colloq.
U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Soldierlike</ent>⟦br⟧
